<p>I agree with your first paragraph, but your second paragraph ignores the facts that Kavanaugh isn’t any Joe Sixpack and the Senate proceedings are not a criminal OR a civil case. He is a judge with lifetime tenure who is being considered for the highest court in the US, again with lifetime tenure.</p>
